00006 *******************************************************************************
00007 * DESCRIPTION                                                                 *
00008 * Computes the integral of the Green's function normal derivative H for one   * 
00009 * element when the collocation point is one of the nodes of the integration   *
00010 * element, and returns the values for all shape functions in vector Int[].    *
00011 * Uses element subdivision and standard Gauss-Legendre quadrature integration.*
00012 * Works for quadratic interpolation in triangular elements (6-noded triangles)*
00013 ******************************************************************************/

00038 #include "integral_tria6.h"

00040 int intSingularH_tria6(const unsigned int FLAG, unsigned int SinNode, 
00041                        double X[6][3], double *Xeval, double *Int, 
00042                        double *normal)
00043 {
00044     const unsigned int NODES_IN_ELEM = 6;
00045     unsigned int i, j, k, m;
00046     double A, A1, A2, B, B1, B2, C, C1, C2, dx, dx1, dx2, dy, dy1, dy2, dz, 
00047             dz1, dz2, J, JL, JL1, JL2, dr, dr1, dr2, tmp, W, M1, M2, M3, U1, U2, U3;
00048     double L[2], L1[2], L2[2], N[6], N1[6], N2[6], XL[3], XL1[3], XL2[3];
00049     double xs[3][3][2];
00050  
00051     /* Initialize */
00052     if(FLAG == 0) for(i = 0; i < NODES_IN_ELEM; i++) Int[i] = 0.0;
00053     else for(i = 0; i < 18; i++) Int[i] = 0.0;
00054 
00055     /* Reorder so that singularity is at node 5 */
00056     if(SinNode == 1){
00057         for(i = 0; i < 3; i++){
00058             shift(X[4][i],X[0][i],X[2][i]);
00059             shift(X[5][i],X[1][i],X[3][i]);         
00060         }
00061     }
00062     else if(SinNode == 3){
00063         for(i = 0; i < 3; i++){
00064             shift(X[4][i],X[2][i],X[0][i]);
00065             shift(X[3][i],X[1][i],X[5][i]);
00066         }
00067     }
00068     
00069     /* Setup 3 initial triangles */
00070     xs[0][0][0] = 1.0;  xs[0][0][1] = 0.0;
00071     xs[0][1][0] = 0.5;  xs[0][1][1] = 0.5;
00072     xs[0][2][0] = 0.5;  xs[0][2][1] = 0.0;
00073 
00074     xs[1][0][0] = 0.5;  xs[1][0][1] = 0.0;
00075     xs[1][1][0] = 0.5;  xs[1][1][1] = 0.5;
00076     xs[1][2][0] = 0.0;  xs[1][2][1] = 0.5;
00077     
00078     xs[2][0][0] = 0.5;  xs[2][0][1] = 0.5;
00079     xs[2][1][0] = 0.0;  xs[2][1][1] = 1.0;
00080     xs[2][2][0] = 0.0;  xs[2][2][1] = 0.5;
00081     
00082     /* Start subdivision loop */
00083     J = 1.0;
00084     for(m = 0; m < NSUBDIVISIONS; m++){
00085         J = J*0.25;
00086     
00087         /* Integrate over the 3 triangles furthest away from the singularity */
00088         for(i = 0; i < 3; i++){
00089             
00090             /* Integrate over each triangle using Gauss-Legendre quadrature */
00091             for(j = 0; j < TSNGAUSS; j++){
00092                 M1 = TSGauss[j][0];
00093                 M2 = TSGauss[j][1];
00094                 M3 = 1.0 - M1 - M2;
00095                 W = TSGauss[j][2];
00096 
00097                 /**************************************************** 
00098                 * Get L and N as a function of (M1,M2). This is the *
00099                 * transformation between the unit triangle (M1,M2)  *
00100                 * and the smaller subtriangle (L1,L2)               *
00101                 ****************************************************/
00102                 if(SinNode%2 == 1){
00103                     L[0] = xs[i][0][0]*M1 + xs[i][1][0]*M2 + xs[i][2][0]*M3;
00104                     L[1] = xs[i][0][1]*M1 + xs[i][1][1]*M2 + xs[i][2][1]*M3;
00105                     shape_tria6(L,N);
00106                     JL = X2L_tria6(X,XL,L,N);
00107                     
00108                     /* Auxiliar quantities */
00109                     dx = Xeval[0] - XL[0];
00110                     dy = Xeval[1] - XL[1];
00111                     dz = Xeval[2] - XL[2];
00112                     dr = sqrt(dx*dx + dy*dy + dz*dz);
00113                     A = J*JL*W/(dr*dr*dr);
00114                     
00115                     if(FLAG == 0){
00116                         A = A*(dx*normal[0] + dy*normal[1] + dz*normal[2]);
00117                         for(k = 0; k < NODES_IN_ELEM; k++) Int[k] -= A*N[k];
00118                     }
00119                     else{
00120                         C = A*dz;
00121                         B = A*dy;
00122                         A = A*dx;
00123                         for(k = 0; k < NODES_IN_ELEM; k++){
00124                             Int[k*3] += A*N[k];
00125                             Int[k*3+1] += B*N[k];
00126                             Int[k*3+2] += C*N[k];
00127                         }
00128                     }
00129                 }
00130                 else{
00131                     if(SinNode == 2){
00132                         U1 = 0.5*M3; U2 = M1 + 0.5*M3; U3 = 1.0 - U1 - U2;
00133                         L1[0] = xs[i][0][0]*U1 + xs[i][1][0]*U2 + xs[i][2][0]*U3;
00134                         L1[1] = xs[i][0][1]*U1 + xs[i][1][1]*U2 + xs[i][2][1]*U3;
00135                         U1 = M1 + 0.5*M3; U2 = M3; U3 = 1.0 - U1 - U2;
00136                         L2[0] = xs[i][0][0]*U1 + xs[i][1][0]*U2 + xs[i][2][0]*U3;
00137                         L2[1] = xs[i][0][1]*U1 + xs[i][1][1]*U2 + xs[i][2][1]*U3;
00138                     }
00139                     else if(SinNode == 4){
00140                         U1 = M1; U2 = 0.5*M3; U3 = 1.0 - U1 - U2;
00141                         L1[0] = xs[i][0][0]*U1 + xs[i][1][0]*U2 + xs[i][2][0]*U3;
00142                         L1[1] = xs[i][0][1]*U1 + xs[i][1][1]*U2 + xs[i][2][1]*U3;
00143                         U1 = M1; U2 = M2 + 0.5*M3; U3 = 1.0 - U1 - U2;
00144                         L2[0] = xs[i][0][0]*U1 + xs[i][1][0]*U2 + xs[i][2][0]*U3;
00145                         L2[1] = xs[i][0][1]*U1 + xs[i][1][1]*U2 + xs[i][2][1]*U3;
00146                     }
00147                     else{
00148                         U1 = 0.5*M3; U2 = M1; U3 = 1.0 - U1 - U2;
00149                         L1[0] = xs[i][0][0]*U1 + xs[i][1][0]*U2 + xs[i][2][0]*U3;
00150                         L1[1] = xs[i][0][1]*U1 + xs[i][1][1]*U2 + xs[i][2][1]*U3;
00151                         U1 = M1 + 0.5*M3; U2 = M2; U3 = 1.0 - U1 - U2;
00152                         L2[0] = xs[i][0][0]*U1 + xs[i][1][0]*U2 + xs[i][2][0]*U3;
00153                         L2[1] = xs[i][0][1]*U1 + xs[i][1][1]*U2 + xs[i][2][1]*U3;
00154                     }
00155                     shape_tria6(L1,N1);
00156                     shape_tria6(L2,N2);
00157                     JL1 = X2L_tria6(X,XL1,L1,N1);
00158                     JL2 = X2L_tria6(X,XL2,L2,N2);   
00159 
00160                     /* Auxiliar quantities */
00161                     dx1 = Xeval[0] - XL1[0];
00162                     dy1 = Xeval[1] - XL1[1];
00163                     dz1 = Xeval[2] - XL1[2];
00164                     dx2 = Xeval[0] - XL2[0];
00165                     dy2 = Xeval[1] - XL2[1];
00166                     dz2 = Xeval[2] - XL2[2];
00167                     dr1 = sqrt(dx1*dx1 + dy1*dy1 + dz1*dz1);
00168                     dr2 = sqrt(dx2*dx2 + dy2*dy2 + dz2*dz2);
00169                     A1 = 0.5*J*JL1*W/(dr1*dr1*dr1);
00170                     A2 = 0.5*J*JL2*W/(dr2*dr2*dr2);
00171                     
00172                     if(FLAG == 0){
00173                         A1 = A1*(dx1*normal[0] + dy1*normal[1] + dz1*normal[2]);
00174                         A2 = A2*(dx2*normal[0] + dy2*normal[1] + dz2*normal[2]);
00175 
00176                         for(k = 0; k < NODES_IN_ELEM; k++) Int[k] -= A1*N1[k] + A2*N2[k];
00177                     }
00178                     else{
00179                         C1 = A1*dz1;
00180                         B1 = A1*dy1;
00181                         A1 = A1*dx1;
00182                         C2 = A2*dz2;
00183                         B2 = A2*dy2;
00184                         A2 = A2*dx2;
00185                         for(k = 0; k < NODES_IN_ELEM; k++){
00186                             Int[k*3] += A1*N1[k] + A2*N2[k];
00187                             Int[k*3+1] += B1*N1[k] + B2*N2[k];
00188                             Int[k*3+2] += C1*N1[k] + B2*N2[k];
00189                         }
00190                     }
00191                 }
00192             }
00193         }
00194    
00195         /* Set triangles for new subdivision */
00196         for(i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
00197             for(j = 0; j < 3; j++){
00198                 xs[i][j][0] = xs[i][j][0]*0.5;
00199                 xs[i][j][1] = xs[i][j][1]*0.5;
00200             }
00201         }
00202     }
00203 
00204     /* Unscramble node contributions to return them in their right places */
00205     if(FLAG == 0){
00206         if(SinNode == 1){
00207             shift(Int[2],Int[0],Int[4]);
00208             shift(Int[3],Int[1],Int[5]);            
00209         }
00210         else if(SinNode == 3){
00211             shift(Int[0],Int[2],Int[4]);
00212             shift(Int[5],Int[1],Int[3]);
00213         }
00214     }
00215     else{
00216         if(SinNode == 1){
00217             for(i = 0; i < 3; i++){
00218                 shift(Int[6+i],Int[i],Int[12+i]);
00219                 shift(Int[9+i],Int[3+i],Int[15+i]);         
00220             }
00221         }
00222         else if(SinNode == 3){
00223             for(i = 0; i < 3; i++){
00224                 shift(Int[i],Int[6+i],Int[12+i]);
00225                 shift(Int[15+i],Int[3+i],Int[9+i]);
00226             }
00227         }
00228     }
00229 
00230     return 0;
00231 }
